				<td colspan="2"><span>I believe the stone upgrades go something like this:
<br />

<br />
No stats upgrades at all till you have 3 wins in each.
<br />

<br />
Every 10 wins in any theme will gain you 2 hp/mana from 10 wins to 40 and 3 hp/mana from 50 to 80.  So 4*2*5+4*3*5 = 100 hp/mana on a maxxed stone.
<br />

<br />
Every 10 hp/mana you earn will gain you +1 to ac/resists.
<br />

<br />
After you hail the npc enough times to get an upgrade, re-equip your charm to see the upgrade.</span></td>
